sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as KServe V2 Client
    participant RestProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Marshaler as CustomJSONPb<br/>Marshaler/Unmarshaler
    participant Gateway as gRPC-Gateway<br/>Reverse Proxy
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (POST /v2/models/{model_name}/infer)

    Client->>RestProxy: POST /v2/models/{model_name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Optional TLS
    RestProxy->>Marshaler: Decode JSON request body<br/>Parse tensor data (INT, FP, BYTES)<br/>Handle base64 BYTES, multi-dim arrays
    Marshaler->>Gateway: Decoded InferRequest proto
    Gateway->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelInfer()<br/>8033/TCP localhost<br/>Optional TLS
    ModelMesh-->>Gateway: gRPC InferResponse
    Gateway-->>Marshaler: Proto response
    Marshaler-->>RestProxy: Marshal to JSON<br/>Serialize tensor contents
    RestProxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON Response<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request (GET /v2/models/{name})

    Client->>RestProxy: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Optional TLS
    RestProxy->>Gateway: Route to ModelMetadata
    Gateway->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelMetadata()<br/>8033/TCP localhost<br/>Optional TLS
    ModelMesh-->>Gateway: ModelMetadataResponse
    Gateway-->>RestProxy: Proto response
    RestProxy-->>Client: HTTP 200 JSON<br/>Model metadata
